{
  "stem": "26672.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would imagine so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know exactly what the-- my oldest sister went to gymnasium, which is all year high school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Um, I seem to remember she almost finished, because she worked for my father's business parlor at the time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What else she did after, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As far as I know, they were still in-- learning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whether they-- I don't think they went to-- to high schools at that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe they went to girl's [? sams ?] or something like that, yeah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was always tested by my father on a Friday night-- excuse me-- what I've learned.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Actually he paid for it, because he wanted to know what I learned.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't, um-- education, like even today, a lot of it is private.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's not state aided.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It certainly wasn't in Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm sure it wasn't state aided.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I'm sure I didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sure I didn't, but I was very friendly with the, um, the son of our town rabbis.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we always learned together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE], I went to his father, and he came to my father always to be tested.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was mostly on a Friday night or Shabbos depending on when there was a-- it was Friday night.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the summer, it was Shabbos afternoon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I remember the walk going through to him, yes, yeah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't remember exactly the detail, but I would imagine when you get up in the morning you had certain prayers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sure I must have gone with my father if I was old enough to go with him to [?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Shul ?], uh, like so many today.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
